ills necessary to become productive citizens and life-long learners. It is my honor and privilege to serve our great community as we strive for educational excellence.       Chad Farnsworth Superintendent of Schools   Under Florida law, e-mails are public records. If you do not want your e-mail released in response to a public records request, do not send electronic mail to the BCSD. Instead, contact this office by phone. 501 W. Washington Street | Starke, Florida, 32091 | Phone: 904.966.6800 The Bradford County School District is an Equal Opportunity Employer. We consider applicants for all positions without regard to race, color, national origin, gender, age, disability, marital status, sexual orientation, religion or any other legally protected status. Designed by The Net Group Online.
